        <div id="wrap1">
        <h1>Tooltip - Joomla! template by BonusThemes.com</h1>
        <div class="wrap2">
        <img style="padding-left: 10px;float:right; background-color: #fff;border:1px solid #CFCFCF;margin:0px 20px 2px 20px;border:none;" src="../templates/bt_tooltip/template_thumbnail.png" border="0" alt="Logo" /><p>The online purchase of machinery and tools presents a significant upward trend in recent years, similar to that which occurred in the market of IT products in the past decade. Not only individuals or hobbyists, but professionals choose the internet to investigate, compare and ultimately buy the best price tools of their choice. The tooltip, is a template created by BonusThemes, for the needs of electronic stores of tools and machineries.</p>

<p>With 3 different color skins, pleasant and functional design, so as not to bore you, but to facilitate searching through key product categories and subcategories, it has all those features that will make your online store to win many fanatic customers.</p>

<p>Each product is presented with one or more photos and accompanied by a description, specifications and reviews. On the main page there is a big slide baner which can be significant promotions, new arrivals, seasonal products, etc. Product categories developed both in the vertical left column and horizontally using representative photographs. Simultaneously been provided separate areas for baners communicating transport policy, payment methods, subscribing to newsletters, etc.</p>

<p>The soul of tooltip, is reliable and well established online store virtuemart module in combination with the content management system K2, create an efficient and flexible approach electronic commerce.</p>

<p>The customization capabilities of the tooltip, make it ideal for many other e-shops, such as: electric appliances, automotive parts, cooling and heating, exercise equipment, etc.</p>

<p>Learn more about the tooltip through the live preview and add it in your cart. Soon your own products will be in the basket of the most discerning buyers!</p>
        <h3>Features</h3>
        <ul>
        <li>HTML 5, CSS 3</li>
        <li>Full compatible with Joomla! 2.5.x and Joomla! 3.x</li>
        <li>RTL (right to left) support</li>
        <li>2 Menu types: 1) Css, 2) Drop Down (Ajax / JQuery)</li>
        <li>Collapsible Module Positions</li>
        <li>Advanced Content Typography</li>
        <li>Disable option for mainbody appearance on front page.</li>
        <li>Improved style of Joomla! Core system pages.</li>
        <li>Error 404 page</li>
        <li>Offline page</li>
        <li>K2! compatible</li>
        <li>Virtuemart compatible</li>
        <li>Adjustable settings from the Template Manager</li>
        <li>Adjustable position widths from the Template Manager</li>
        <li>Quickstart Package included</li>
        <li>Png Sources included</li>
        <li>Lightweight, modern and very fast-loading design.</li>
        <li>Clean, Simple and Stylish look</li>
        <li>Fully compatible IE9+, Firefox, Safari, Opera, Chrome.</li>
        <li>W3C XHTML 1.0 Transitional, W3C CSS Valid.</li>
        </ul>			
        - View Tooltip in <a href="http://www.bonusthemes.com/demo/?template=tooltip" target="_blank">live demo</a><br>
        - For support visit our <a href="http://www.bonusthemes.com/forum/index" target="_blank">Forum</a>.
        </div>
